OL,4,CLiverpool City Council: Staff at
OL,5,Ccouncil feared speaking out
OL,6, Staff felt intimidated about speaking
OL,7, out on failings at a city council and
OL,8, there were "credible" fears for their
OL,9, safety if they did, an inspector says.
OL,11,FMax Caller told the BBC his report into
OL,12,Fproblems at Liverpool City Council left
OL,13,Fout the names of those who spoke to him
OL,14,Fbecause they worried about reprisals.
OL,16,FThe report was published in March, and
OL,17,Fa police investigation continues.
OL,19,FThe council has said it accepts all the
OL,20,Freport's findings and it was one of the
OL,21,Fmost difficult periods in its history.
